column5: After a real slow start the water started to reach that majic temp and the fish wer on 0 crappie for 9am to 12pm from 12pm to 2pm 80-100 slabs sorry no pics but a full tummy Dan
We found it slow yesterday as well, never did find that "magic temperature" but we did get a few later in the day.  Hopefully today will be better with warmer weather.
